# field-recording-mirror is a pure static site — there are no runtime secrets.
# This file exists so the meta-prompt convention is honoured and so future
# build-time configuration (e.g. an analytics opt-in flag) has a home.

# Overrides for vite.config.ts. Leave unset unless you know why.
# VITE_APP_BASE=/field-recording-mirror/
# VITE_APP_VERSION=
# VITE_GIT_COMMIT=
# VITE_BUILT_AT=
